fix(reports): View Report PDF visible by default + readable ticket-id pill

- getClientConfig now auto-derives WEEKLY_REPORT_PUBLIC_URL and
  FULL_REPORT_PUBLIC_URL from BACKUP_REPO+BACKUP_BRANCH when the
  operator hasn't filled them in. Login + dashboard "View Report"
  pills now appear automatically once FEATURE_WEEKLY_REPORT_BACKUP
  is on (no extra tunable wiring required).
- Login page button restyled from a vertical icon column to a small
  sleek red PDF pill that matches the existing "Open in Sheets" pill
  aesthetic on submitted-issues.html.
- Committee/builder/admin dashboards now show a "View Full Report"
  red PDF pill in the header bar (admin previously had no entry).
- Ticket-id pill (rendered everywhere via window.titleWithTicketId)
  switched from amber-300 text on slate-900 to slate-900 text on a
  bright amber-400 to yellow-300 gradient. ~13:1 contrast (WCAG AAA),
  readable for older eyes, still inside the project's gold theme.
